               2 Sam. 4.5. and Iſhboſheth Sauls ſon, that was ſet up by Abner his Uncle, was cut off by Baanah and Rechab, two of the chief Commanders in the Army.) His firſt care, I ſay, after the ſetling of his Kingdome, was with ſolemn joy and triumph to bring back the ark of God. to his own City, and its proper reſting place.
